## Learning Modes

Rooted Labs operates under three modes:

### 1. School Mode (B2B)
- Teacher controls progression
- Discussion and unplugged activities are mandatory
- Levels unlock only after teacher confirmation

### 2. Home Mode (B2C)
- System controls progression
- Rule-based unlocks (time, completion, reflection)
- No teacher dependency

### 3. AI Mode (Future)
- AI adapts pacing and hints
- Built using data from Modes 1 & 2

⚠️ Mode changes do NOT change content or structure.
